of passion, actually, that you find.

00:12:15.450 --> 00:12:18.220
But I think that's one
of the things that he--

00:12:18.220 --> 00:12:24.150
that he's so amazingly does,
and that-- that's rare I think.

00:12:24.150 --> 00:12:25.450
&gt;&gt; Michael Abramowitz: Adam?

00:12:25.450 --> 00:12:26.750
&gt;&gt; Adam Gopnic: Yeah.

00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:28.050
