dispassionate voice

00:13:14.500 --> 00:13:19.040
as a scientific observer of human
experience and human quality.

00:13:19.040 --> 00:13:21.590
I think it's the way those two
things are constantly intention

00:13:21.590 --> 00:13:26.770
on his work that makes him not
just a witness but a great author.

00:13:26.770 --> 00:13:28.070
&gt;&gt; Michael Abramowitz: Right.

