00:17:43.650 --> 00:17:44.950
&gt;&gt; Michael Abramowitz: Right.

00:17:44.950 --> 00:17:47.560
Adam, you've written in
the past about translation.

00:17:47.560 --> 00:17:51.590
What is your sense of the project
here in terms of what's impressive

00:17:51.590 --> 00:17:55.140
from the point of view of
a translation perspective?

00:17:55.140 --> 00:17:57.230
&gt;&gt; Adam Gopnic: Well, I have the
