00:19:03.610 --> 00:19:04.910
&gt;&gt; Ann Goldstein: Yeah.

00:19:04.910 --> 00:19:06.210
&gt;&gt; Adam Gopnic: -- in the film.

00:19:06.210 --> 00:19:07.510
