00:26:29.780 --> 00:26:32.580
It's very--

00:26:32.580 --> 00:26:33.880
&gt;&gt; Ann Goldstein: Yell.

00:26:33.880 --> 00:26:35.180
&gt;&gt; Michael Abramowitz:
So I'm really kind

00:26:35.180 --> 00:26:39.740
