That's one of the things that--

00:27:06.780 --> 00:27:08.080
&gt;&gt; Ann Goldstein: Right.

00:27:08.080 --> 00:27:09.380
&gt;&gt; Adam Gopnic: --
that occurs, right?

00:27:09.380 --> 00:27:12.110
It goes from a kind of O Fish
