only question, was do you believe

00:54:09.340 --> 00:54:14.920 position:56%
that Primo Levi wrote these books so
he could teach us a lesson of trying

00:54:14.920 --> 00:54:19.190
to repeat our mistakes in the past?

00:54:19.190 --> 00:54:20.870
&gt;&gt; Ann Goldstein:I don't think
Primo Levi would ever have thought

00:54:20.870 --> 00:54:23.620
that he was teaching
anybody a lesson, but--

00:54:23.620 --> 00:54:27.530
although he was very
interested in talking to--

00:54:27.530 --> 00:54:31.760
in talking to children
and in visiting schools.

00:54:31.760 --> 00:54:36.150
But I think that-- I
guess that's the lesson.

00:54:36.150 --> 00:54:38.040
&gt;&gt; Levi wanted to understand how--

