00:55:49.830 --> 00:55:53.120
in the little film we saw a moment
ago and it's stomatic in all

00:55:53.120 --> 00:55:57.130
of Levi's work is that
the pathogens of fascism,

00:55:57.130 --> 00:56:00.100
what happened in his view
are sort of omnipresent.

00:56:00.100 --> 00:56:05.660
These-- They're talking about them
being around in the '80s in Italy

00:56:05.660 --> 00:56:09.470
and that his view is, is that,
we make a mistake if we see it

00:56:09.470 --> 00:56:14.290
