that the pathogens of exclusion,

00:56:31.300 --> 00:56:35.080
the pathogens of racism, the
pathogens of indifference,

00:56:35.080 --> 00:56:38.360
pathogens of indifference
to what's going on around us

00:56:38.360 --> 00:56:41.390
